title: Supreme Snowboarding
description:
Supreme Snowboarding, release 1.033


Language: English, Frensh, German, Finnish


Works with XP and Vista


Ripped directly from original CD with IsoBuster.


Mount in Daemon Tools, install and play - the crack is not needed

                            BUT

if you want to play without the CD-image in Daemon Tools you must use the crack.
Just run it in the installation-folder. The crack tells you what to do.


                         IMPORTANT!!

A big minus with the no-cd-crack is that the intro movie, some background pictures and the music during the game doesn't work. If you want this you must play with the CD.


Enjoy the game!
